Living the Whitsunday dream 🌊

New Moon Vibes 🌚 

The perfection of this New Moon in the sign of Pisces ♓ is what dreams are made of.
The power of belief has to be stronger than the power of your doubts. They say if you can dream it, you can accomplish it. 
With everything unfolding in the world at the moment, the human psyche is in turmoil. The question is can we believe in what we can't yet see, or will the density of the world and the perceptions that are sold to us be our undoing....

My journey lately has been to undo most things that I have percieved to be reality...I know I am the creator...yet have stumbled when I create experiences that are opposite to what I desire. As I swim to the surface of a depth of despare I didn't know I could fall into, the work on my own personal consciousness to get myself out of the hole I had dug is beginning to bare fruit. The fruit is a glimmer of light that shines through cracks of awakening, previously hidden as I distracted myself in the frivolities of life. 
I choose to believe that underneath the despair of what is unfolding is a break through. 
The 'any day now' kinda break through.

I challenge you to flip your perspective on what you believe is reality, to go beyond the conditioned experience and begin to step into a New World 🌎  One that you create and believe in. One that comes from source....and all source is LOVE ❤  Connecting to love is our only salvation right now 

I believe humankind is ready for the shift. I believe we have been working towards this our whole life 

And so it is 🕉

This is Anne Marsh holding the trousers she was splitting the seams on up and down the legs almost 16 years ago. 

Anne is now 65 years young, with two chronic health conditions which, she was told, would prevent her from being slim again. 

The menopause intervened too plus an accident, and 2 hip replacementments!

Anne understands what it’s like to battle those demons and has succeeded magnificently! 

Thanks for sharing Anne!

Started on Shakes and Boosters. In March I was a lb away from 15 stone. Biggest I've ever been. I was down in myself and purely hated myself. I came across Juice Plus and started my shakes and boosters. I lost a stone and a half and started to feel more confident in myself and more energy. I then chose to use Berry capsules and keep my boosters. I carried on losing weight and feeling better in myself. I've still got along way to go until I reach my original weight before having my little boy. But I'm so happy with myself now. 🙂 In march I was 14 stone 13lbs. And now 5 months later I'm now 12 stone 6lbs. I am so glad I found this plan and would not change a thing. . 🙂 ❤

#thursdaythinspiration... My book is crammed full and stuck together with stickers and sellotape and even has an extra page glued in as I ran out of space.....In three years and seven months I've not missed going to group once which is where I'd gone wrong so many times before and as @towers_weightjourney says, it's all about being consistent.
